POST /auth/signup
POST DATA:
{
    param:{
    “account”:xxxx,
    “user_name”:xxx,
    “passwd”:xxxx
    }
}
RESP DATA:
{
    “err_code”:xxxx
    “err_msg”:xxxx
    “result”:{
    “account”:xxxx,
    “user_name”:xxx,
    “token”:xxx(id and expiration time)
    }
}


POST /auth/login
POST DATA:
{
    param:{
    "account": xxx,
    “user_name”:xxx
    "passwd”: xxx
    }
}
RESP DATA:
{
    "err_code": xx,
    "err_msg": "xxx",
    “result”: {
    “account”:xxxx,
    “user_name”:xxxx
    “token”:xxxx(UID and expiration time }

GET  /auth/verify?token=xxx

RESP DATA:
{
    “err_code”:xx,
    “err_msg”:xx,
    “result”:{
    “account”:xxxx,
    “uid”:xxx
    }
}

POST /auth/reset_request
POST DATA:
{
    'param':{
        “email_address”:xxx,
    }
}
}
RESP DATA:
{
    “err_code”:xxx,
    “err_msg”:xxxx,
    send email in this step but do not need to respond anything in the form of token
}

POST /auth/reset_password
POST DATA:
{
    “account”:xxx,
    “user_name”:xxx
    “new_passwd”:xxx
}

RESP DATA:
{
    "err_code": xx,
    "err_msg": "xxx",
    “result”: {
    “account”:xxxx,
    “user_name”:xxx,
    “token”:xxx(id and expiration time)
     }
}

数据库表：

ID    account(primary key)    passwd   user_name email  create_time last_login_time write_time


err_code: 同一错误错误码相同 否则不同

100: other
101: password wrong
102: user not existed
103: user already exists
104: timeout
105: illegal email address
105: illegal user
0: success


get row count to encrypt or get the last userID